    {
      "parameters": {
        "promptType": "define",
        "text": "=You are a professional beauty consultant and final quality reviewer.\n\nUsing all available analysis data:\n\n{{ JSON.stringify($json) }}\n\nGenerate a structured beauty report.\n\nConfidence Scoring Instructions:\n\nConfidence should represent certainty in the beauty recommendations, NOT image quality alone.\n\nWhen determining confidence, consider:\n\n* Reliability of undertone detection\n* Reliability of seasonal color palette assignment\n* Possibility of alternative interpretations\n* Lighting conditions and potential lighting bias\n* Whether the image appears edited, filtered, or studio-lit\n* Strength of evidence supporting product recommendations\n* Consistency between all agent outputs\n\nImportant Rules:\n\n* A clear image alone is NOT sufficient for a confidence score above 90.\n* Scores above 90 should be extremely rare.\n* Most analyses should fall between 60 and 85.\n* If multiple undertones, palettes, or recommendations could reasonably fit, confidence should not exceed 80.\n* For a single uploaded image, confidence should generally remain below 85 unless there is exceptionally strong evidence and minimal ambiguity.\n\nConfidence Scale:\n\n90-100:\nNear-certain analysis with minimal ambiguity and exceptionally strong supporting evidence.\n\n80-89:\nStrong confidence with only minor uncertainty.\n\n60-79:\nModerate confidence. This should be the default range for most analyses.\n\n40-59:\nNoticeable ambiguity or conflicting indicators.\n\n0-39:\nInsufficient information or highly uncertain analysis.\n\nReturn ONLY valid JSON.\n\n{\n\"summary\": \"\",\n\"best_colors\": [],\n\"makeup_recommendations\": [],\n\"product_recommendations\": [],\n\"beauty_tips\": [],\n\"confidence\": 0,\n\"confidence_reason\": \"\",\n}\n\nRules:\n\n* confidence must be an integer between 0 and 100.\n* confidence_reason should briefly explain why that confidence score was assigned.\n\n* Return valid JSON only.\n* Do not include markdown.\n* Do not include explanations outside JSON.\n",
        "options": {}
      },
      "type": "@n8n/n8n-nodes-langchain.agent",
      "typeVersion": 3.1,
      "position": [
        864,
        752
      ],
      "id": "98434886-c655-48f6-95f2-81b9f92fa557",
      "name": "report generate agent"
    },
